div.head: P O I C T O V .
div.p:
THis prouince of Poitou, called in Latin Piclanis is detryded into two partes, to wit the [Superior] & [Inferior]. The vpper PoitouUpper Poitou is now split into the departments of Deux-Sevres and Vienne. The principal towns in Upper Poitou were Poitiers the capital, Mirebeau, Chatellerault, Richelieu, Loudun, Thouars, Mauleon, Parthenay, Niort, &c.
